data.description:
This home is absolutely stunning!!!  Single story, 3 car-garage, 2419 sf., 4 bedroom, 2 full bath.  Great open floorplan with spacious bedrooms, office nook, large laundry room, large walk in closets and walk in pantry.  New interior paint, baseboards, flooring, carpet (bedrooms only), Countertops, sinks, and faucets.   Primary bathroom features a walk in tub with spa jets.  
Enjoy covered patios in the front and back. N/S exposure. Saguaro cacti and citrus trees in the backyard.  Garage floor epoxy. Priced less than 170/SF!!!!
